body:
@HumanEquivalentUnit, regarding the inconsistent handling of stderr output, see:

* #3996
* #4002

@zachChilders, as an aside: there is no need to use `Start-Process` to invoke _console/terminal programs_ such as `cmake` in a _synchronous_ manner - that's what direct invocation is for. See [this Stack Overflow answer](https://stackoverflow.com/a/51334633/45375) for more information.
